responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "ADF6C92E4313DA69738A02A35D797D75", "It would seem not even death can release one from the clutches of the Raven Plague. I will have to organize a Pyre Militia to burn their remains and all that they touch. We thank you for your service. For Greater Glory!")
